text:
Hot Drunk Girl Does Cartwheels During DUI Stop, Kicks Officer In The Nuts 5 hours ago share 
Drunk girls are the worst! She was found passed out in her car, and wouldn't stop doing cartwheels when the officer attempted a field sobriety test. After all was said & done she was taken in and allegedly tried to kick the officer in the nuts. 
On the other hand, she has a pretty great Instagram account...
